      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly with plenty of power, and the transmission shifts exactly as it should, providing a reliable and comfortable driving experience. The interior is clean with only minor signs of use, and the exterior paint still holds a nice shine, though you may find a few small blemishes typical of a pre-owned car. It\u2019s a solid, dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
